### Registrar un nuevo deudor
POST http://localhost:3000/deudores
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cuit": "20123456789",
  "situacion": 3,
  "monto": 150000
}

### Registrar otro deudor
POST http://localhost:3000/deudores
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cuit": "30765432109",
